The RTE Symbol Inserter is titled "Insert Custom Character" - it uses this for the tooltip, the popup window name, and the page title.

However, the popup allows the user to select from a static list of predefined symbols.  There is no way for the user to define and use their own characters.

So then why is this feature titled "Insert Custom Character"?  A title such as "Insert Symbol" would make more sense, and better reflect the actual functionality provided.

