In the [http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Adding+a+Navigation+Sidebar] page, the line that reads

{code}<table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5">{code}

should be replaced by

{code}<table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5" width="100%">{code}

This will ensure that the page contents make use of the available width. For instance, a page with \{panel} macro may not expand to the right edge of the page.

